Cencosud Is in Talks to Sell Consumer Loans, Financiero Reports

-- B y   J a m e s   A t t w o o d
-- 
2011-04-15T11:29:12Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-04-15/cencosud-is-in-talks-to-sell-consumer-loans-financiero-reports.html
Cencosud SA,  Chile ’s biggest
retailer by sales, is negotiating the sale of $400 million in
consumer loans with five banks to help fund investments, Diario
Financiero reported.  The transaction may be finalized in the coming days, the
Santiago-based newspaper reported, citing people familiar with
the transaction that it didn’t identify.   Cencosud’s public relations representatives didn’t answer a
phone call seeking comment or immediately respond to an e-mailed
request for comment.  Click here for web link  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
